se.chalmers.ait.dat215.project
Class Order

java.lang.Object
  se.chalmers.ait.dat215.project.Order

public class Order
extends java.lang.Object

The Order class represents an order to the store. An order is made up of an ordernumber, a date and a list of ShoppingItems. Normally, there should be no need to modifiy an order since it is created automatically when the customer places an order. Therefore, the most interesting methods are the getters that gives access to the different parts of an order.
